Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.97,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs72\pos(365,362)}Doubt
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.72,0:00:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to admit that I was rather surprised, Ryuuga, {\alpha&HFF&}to be invited to play tennis with you so that we could get to know each other better.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.35,0:00:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to admit that I was rather surprised, Ryuuga, to be invited to play tennis with you so that we could get to know each other better.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.85,0:00:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has this caused a problem for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.73,0:00:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all... {\alpha&HFF&}but were you aware of how skilled I am when you asked me to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.97,0:00:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all... but were you aware of how skilled I am when you asked me to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.83,0:00:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay, Yagami-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.33,0:00:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to be the Junior Champion of England.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.73,0:00:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I ask him, "Does that mean you're English?", will he think that I'm attempting to question him because I am Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.88,0:00:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind. {\alpha&HFF&}I'll just give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.77,0:00:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind. I'll just give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.39,0:00:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you brought up in England?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.76,0:00:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've lived in England for about five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.60,0:00:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wouldn't worry about it, {\alpha&HFF&}there's nothing about that which will compromise my identity as L.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.39,0:00:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wouldn't worry about it, there's nothing about that which will compromise my identity as L.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.67,0:00:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.30,0:00:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're fine with the winner being whoever wins the first set of six games, I assume?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.23,0:00:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.07,0:01:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is strictly a friendly tennis match.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to use this to help me judge whether he's Kira or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.70,0:01:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kira does supposedly hate to lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.00,0:01:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fifteen - love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.77,0:01:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, Ryuuga, {\alpha&HFF&}you're getting serious already?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.45,0:01:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, Ryuuga, you're getting serious already?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.48,0:01:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He who takes the initiative wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.88,0:01:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "you can't say"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.33,0:01:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm extremely sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.59,0:01:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Under L's orders, I can't tell anyone outside the Investigative Headquarters, even if you are the Deputy Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.75,0:01:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even tell me what you're doing, and where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.16,0:01:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm extremely sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.51,0:01:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Yagami. {\alpha&HFF&}It's already been four months since this case first came to light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Yagami. It's already been four months since this case first came to light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.96,0:01:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The public believe that the police are incompetent, {\alpha&HFF&}and that L is incompetent.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.51,0:02:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The public believe that the police are incompetent, and that L is incompetent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.30,0:02:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me for saying this, Deputy, {\alpha&HFF&}but can you honestly say that a police force that turns tail and runs scared of Kira is "competent"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.04,0:02:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me for saying this, Deputy, but can you honestly say that a police force that turns tail and runs scared of Kira is "competent"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.26,0:02:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you're well aware of how many of us remained at Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.88,0:02:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're so concerned with public opinion, {\alpha&HFF&}just make sure they don't find out the truth; that the majority of the police force, and especially the leaders, have fled from Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.76,0:02:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're so concerned with public opinion, just make sure they don't find out the truth; that the majority of the police force, and especially the leaders, have fled from Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.82,0:02:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.91,0:02:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.23,0:02:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's L like?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we trust him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.94,0:02:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's far more capable than we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, he's making the moves personally, placing his own life on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.06,0:02:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they meant to be amateurs?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.91,0:02:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.64,0:02:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Yagami Light and Ryuuga Hideki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.24,0:02:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of them enrolled with the top grades.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.35,0:02:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.00,0:02:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although Kira hates to lose, {\alpha&HFF&}the majority of people would want to win in a match, whether they are Kira or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.70,0:02:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although Kira hates to lose, the majority of people would want to win in a match, whether they are Kira or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.98,0:03:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going all out for a win is in keeping with Kira's character? Is this it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.51,0:03:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I purposely lose for that reason — {\alpha&HFF&}thinking that going for a complete victory is Kira-like — then my purposely losing will also be Kira-like, won't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.59,0:03:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I purposely lose for that reason — thinking that going for a complete victory is Kira-like — {\alpha&HFF&}then my purposely losing will also be Kira-like, won't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.43,0:03:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I purposely lose for that reason — thinking that going for a complete victory is Kira-like — then my purposely losing will also be Kira-like, {\alpha&HFF&}won't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.20,0:03:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I purposely lose for that reason — thinking that going for a complete victory is Kira-like — then my purposely losing will also be Kira-like, won't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.74,0:03:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It all comes down to the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way he can use this match to create a profile of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.35,0:03:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The objective of this match lies elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.90,0:03:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, even at tennis... {\alpha&HFF&}I will win this too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, even at tennis... I will win this too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.84,0:03:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See. I knew you would want to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.38,0:03:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Game count, {\alpha&HFF&}four games all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.74,0:03:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Game count, four games all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.66,0:03:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, both a referee and a linesman have appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.06,0:03:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd heard the name Yagami Light before, so I went and looked it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turns out he was the Junior Champion in 2002 and 2003!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During the award ceremony, in his third year of Junior High, he announced; "I'm quitting this hobby at the end of Junior High".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since then, he hasn't participated in any tournaments.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:03:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey! {\alpha&HFF&}Ryuuga-kun is managing to hold his own against a Junior Champion, so what does that make him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.40,0:04:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey! Ryuuga-kun is managing to hold his own against a Junior Champion, so what does that make him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.48,0:04:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can read you, Yagami Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can read your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.82,0:04:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way our friendship is going to deepen thanks to this tennis match.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.03,0:04:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just a ritual formality allowing us to acknowledge that we became better friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.89,0:04:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You believe that I'm using this match to advance my preparations in breaking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet that you'll try to make me say something that only Kira will know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First you'll state that you need to know what information I have on Kira in order to trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're going to talk about the Kira case, {\alpha&HFF&}I'll have to at least request proof that he's actually the one in charge at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.19,0:04:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're going to talk about the Kira case, I'll have to at least request proof that he's actually the one in charge at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why... {\alpha&HFF&}you'll request that I... provide significant proof from a third-party that you are L.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.13,0:04:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why... you'll request that I... {\alpha&HFF&}provide significant proof from a third-party that you are L.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:04:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why... you'll request that I... provide significant proof from a third-party that you are L.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically... {\alpha&HFF&}to take me to the Investigative Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.58,0:05:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically... to take me to the Investigative Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.58,0:05:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&HFF&}Basically... {\alpha&H00}to take you to the Investigative Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.56,0:05:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what the situation, {\alpha&HFF&}you can't win solely by defending.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.81,0:05:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what the situation, you can't win solely by defending.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To win, you need to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Game, set; {\alpha&HFF&}won by Yagami!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.05,0:05:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Game, set; won by Yagami!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.70,0:05:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Six games to four.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.66,0:05:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.72,0:05:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're as good as I expected you to be. {\alpha&HFF&}I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.49,0:05:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're as good as I expected you to be. I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the first time that I've gotten serious over something in a while, {\alpha&HFF&}Ryuuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.39,0:05:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the first time that I've gotten serious over something in a while, Ryuuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thirsty, {\alpha&HFF&}and I have a favor I'd like to ask of you, so shall we stop for a drink after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.34,0:05:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thirsty, and I have a favor I'd like to ask of you, {\alpha&HFF&}so shall we stop for a drink after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thirsty, and I have a favor I'd like to ask of you, so shall we stop for a drink after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, seeing that I lost the game, {\alpha&HFF&}ask away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, seeing that I lost the game, ask away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.39,0:05:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's just one thing I got to mention first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.55,0:05:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suspect that you may be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.86,0:05:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's not a problem, feel free to ask me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.72,0:05:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.34,0:06:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, {\alpha&HFF&}when I say "suspect", it's only about 1%.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, when I say "suspect", it's only about 1%.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.54,0:06:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, {\alpha&HFF&}I'd like to confirm both that you're not Kira, and also the rumors regarding your skills of deduction, before asking you to help with the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, I'd like to confirm both that you're not Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}and also the rumors regarding your skills of deduction, before asking you to help with the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.98,0:06:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, I'd like to confirm both that you're not Kira, and also the rumors regarding your skills of deduction, before asking you to help with the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1%, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.24,0:06:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an excellent way of putting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they suspect me even in the slightest, {\alpha&HFF&}they won't allow me near their Headquarters even if I ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they suspect me even in the slightest, they won't allow me near their Headquarters even if I ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.85,0:06:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've made the first move.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.77,0:06:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This café is a favorite of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.09,0:06:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you sit here, people won't be able to overhear your conversations.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for showing me this place, it's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.77,0:06:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to worry about sitting like that here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to sit like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I sit normally, my investigative abilities decrease by 40%.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.27,0:06:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, {\alpha&HFF&}what's this favor you wanted to ask of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.26,0:07:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's this favor you wanted to ask of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, {\alpha&HFF&}I think I'll leave that until you've confirmed that I'm not Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I think I'll leave that until you've confirmed that I'm not Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.56,0:07:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can go first. Ask me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I don't mean to be rude, {\alpha&HFF&}but would you mind if I tested your skills of deduction?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.00,0:07:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I don't mean to be rude, but would you mind if I tested your skills of deduction?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.05,0:07:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, go right ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.32,0:07:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then. {\alpha&HFF&}First, I'd like you to take a look at these.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.38,0:07:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then. First, I'd like you to take a look at these.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These three are photos of letters; it's thought that Kira controlled criminals in a prison, {\alpha&HFF&}and then, before they died, had them write these.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.46,0:07:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These three are photos of letters; it's thought that Kira controlled criminals in a prison, and then, before they died, had them write these.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.48,0:07:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me hear your opinions about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, this is child's play.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are print numbers on the back of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.51,0:07:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I create the sentence {\alpha&HFF&}"L, did you know Shinigami only eat apples?" without even looking at them, it'll deepen your suspicions, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I create the sentence "L, did you know Shinigami only eat apples?" {\alpha&HFF&}without even looking at them, it'll deepen your suspicions, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I create the sentence "L, did you know Shinigami only eat apples?" without even looking at them, it'll deepen your suspicions, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:08:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But just because I'm able to solve this simple puzzle, {\alpha&HFF&}it won't prove that I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.62,0:08:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But just because I'm able to solve this simple puzzle, it won't prove that I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.01,0:08:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kira can truly manipulate not only the time of death, {\alpha&HFF&}but also the actions of people prior to death, it'd be amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kira can truly manipulate not only the time of death, but also the actions of people prior to death, {\alpha&HFF&}it'd be amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.27,0:08:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kira can truly manipulate not only the time of death, but also the actions of people prior to death, it'd be amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, {\alpha&HFF&}these messages contain hidden messages that seem to be teasing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.71,0:08:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, these messages contain hidden messages that seem to be teasing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.38,0:08:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you take only the top letters from each sentence, and read from left to right, {\alpha&HFF&}it creates another sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.17,0:08:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you take only the top letters from each sentence, and read from left to right, it creates another sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arranging it in the most natural way, it would be... {\alpha&HFF&}"L did you know Shinigami only eat apples", I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.41,0:08:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arranging it in the most natural way, it would be... "L did you know Shinigami only eat apples", I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there are also print numbers on the back of these photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you place them in that order... {\alpha&HFF&}"L, did you know that if they only eat apples, Shinigami",
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.09,0:08:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you place them in that order... "L, did you know that if they only eat apples, Shinigami",
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.07,0:08:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this seems rather unnatural, and I find it hard to believe that this is what Kira wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.82,0:08:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incorrect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.63,0:08:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is in fact a fourth photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.52,0:08:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you include this, it becomes something like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.73,0:09:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"L, did you know that if they only eat apples, Shinigami {\alpha&HFF&}have red hands."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"L, did you know that if they only eat apples, Shinigami have red hands."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.28,0:09:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fourth one is fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't something that I've made a criminal write.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he stupid or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.16,0:09:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my theory is perfect if there are only three photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it was incorrect.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are in fact four. {\alpha&HFF&}It would have been correct if you had accounted for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.97,0:09:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are in fact four. It would have been correct if you had accounted for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.04,0:09:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite the fact that the sentence didn't end, you decided that there were only three photos, and were unable to deduce that there may have been a fourth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.99,0:09:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.18,0:09:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it. He's not trying to test my deduction skills; he's analyzing my reactions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.49,0:09:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I try to challenge him further, I'll be doing exactly what he wants me to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... {\alpha&HFF&}I wasn't able to deduce that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I wasn't able to deduce that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.30,0:09:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, they aren't messages that will bring us any closer to Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.17,0:09:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like Shinigami really exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun, if you were L, {\alpha&HFF&}and were with someone you suspected might be Kira, how would you go about proving it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun, if you were L, and were with someone you suspected might be Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}how would you go about proving it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.79,0:09:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun, if you were L, and were with someone you suspected might be Kira, how would you go about proving it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd make them say something that hasn't been broadcast to the public; {\alpha&HFF&}something that only Kira would know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd make them say something that hasn't been broadcast to the public; something that only Kira would know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.64,0:10:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you are trying to do right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing. {\alpha&HFF&}I've asked many detectives this question, yet most of them need at least a few minutes before they can answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.98,0:10:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing. I've asked many detectives this question, yet most of them need at least a few minutes before they can answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You however, {\alpha&HFF&}were instantaneously able to think as Kira would if they were confronted with someone investigating them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.04,0:10:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You however, were instantaneously able to think as Kira would if they were confronted with someone investigating them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.09,0:10:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your sense of reasoning is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If my ideas are too good, {\alpha&HFF&}it seems like you'll get even more suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If my ideas are too good, it seems like you'll get even more suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.18,0:10:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, {\alpha&HFF&}by 3%.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.84,0:10:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, by 3%.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But at the same time, {\alpha&HFF&}my desire to have you investigate with us has also grown. Even if you are Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But at the same time, my desire to have you investigate with us has also grown. {\alpha&HFF&}Even if you are Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But at the same time, my desire to have you investigate with us has also grown. Even if you are Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.24,0:10:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in a position where it would still benefit me to have you investigate with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand this logic?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I help with the investigation, there's a potential for it to move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.25,0:11:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, if I'm Kira, I might somehow give myself away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.35,0:11:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you can both investigate and interrogate at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's a good idea... {\alpha&HFF&}but I think that you're misunderstanding something here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.94,0:11:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's a good idea... but I think that you're misunderstanding something here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I'm interested in the Kira case, {\alpha&HFF&}and that I also enjoy investigating as a hobby, but I'm not Kira, and I don't want to be killed by Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I'm interested in the Kira case, and that I also enjoy investigating as a hobby, {\alpha&HFF&}but I'm not Kira, and I don't want to be killed by Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.75,0:11:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I'm interested in the Kira case, and that I also enjoy investigating as a hobby, but I'm not Kira, and I don't want to be killed by Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.59,0:11:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you don't have any proof that you're not Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, it'd be strange for only one of us to be investigating the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.01,0:11:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to prove that either of us aren't Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}but since you claim to be L, we should at least be able to prove that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.07,0:11:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to prove that either of us aren't Kira, but {\alpha&HFF&}since you claim to be L, we should at least be able to prove that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to prove that either of us aren't Kira, but since you claim to be L, {\alpha&HFF&}we should at least be able to prove that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.91,0:11:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to prove that either of us aren't Kira, but since you claim to be L, we should at least be able to prove that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.02,0:11:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We could for example get my father or another member of the investigation to identity you in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.81,0:11:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's not possible, then I can't investigate with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're talking a fair amount, Yagami Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.04,0:11:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Typical of someone who doesn't like to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,7%.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.27,0:11:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it really is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.22,0:12:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never said anything about not allowing you to meet the people at the Investigative Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.82,0:12:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.11,0:12:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Currently I'm working both with your father and the others at the Investigative Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.64,0:12:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, if I take you to the Investigative Headquarters, I can get you to cooperate with our investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.59,0:12:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have I understood that correctly?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this guy thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.62,0:12:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.38,0:12:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.30,0:12:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki! {\alpha&HFF&}Something terrible has happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki! Something terrible has happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light! {\alpha&HFF&}Your father...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.55,0:12:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light! Your father...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.60,0:12:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father? {\alpha&HFF&}A heart attack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father? A heart attack?!
Comment: 0,0:12:38.94,0:12:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EYECATCHERS
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll see you tomorrow, and I'll bring some essentials.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.94,0:12:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the rest up to you, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:12:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you're just overworked?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. {\alpha&HFF&}When I first went down I thought that it might be Kira... but it's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.12,0:13:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. When I first went down I thought that it might be Kira... but it's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've probably been overdoing it recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the more because you knew that your son was suspected of being Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.03,0:13:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You even told my father that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.00,0:13:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, {\alpha&HFF&}I've told him everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.87,0:13:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I've told him everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.35,0:13:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the fact that I'm L.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right. {\alpha&HFF&}He is L.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.85,0:13:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right. He is L.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We call him "Ryuuzaki" so that outsiders don't realize it, but without a doubt, he is L.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.32,0:13:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the real L.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what father is saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So if nothing else, he's the L that's been controlling the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can erase him and everyone else on the investigation... {\alpha&HFF&}wait. It's not going to be that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.28,0:13:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can erase him and everyone else on the investigation... wait. {\alpha&HFF&}It's not going to be that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can erase him and everyone else on the investigation... wait. It's not going to be that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.69,0:13:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason to rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.31,0:13:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just need to investigate this situation thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.03,0:13:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, right now, {\alpha&HFF&}I've got to be the Yagami Light who's worried about his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, right now, I've got to be the Yagami Light who's worried about his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, {\alpha&HFF&}Ryuuzaki, have your suspicions about my son lessened now that you've had a chance to talk to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Ryuuzaki, {\alpha&HFF&}have your suspicions about my son lessened now that you've had a chance to talk to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.45,0:14:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Ryuuzaki, have your suspicions about my son lessened now that you've had a chance to talk to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.61,0:14:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say "suspicion", but it was only a very small amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.46,0:14:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me say it once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira has killed twelve FBI agents that were sent to this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.57,0:14:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were all investigating people connected to the Japanese police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of all of them, {\alpha&HFF&}Ray Penber's death stood out as being suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.04,0:14:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of all of them, Ray Penber's death stood out as being suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was one of the ones he was investigating...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.13,0:14:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it can't be helped that I'm a suspect then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as Ryuuga says; {\alpha&HFF&}there's no one else to suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as Ryuuga says; there's no one else to suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your reasoning is quite something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.63,0:14:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's always fast and precise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.94,0:14:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuga, {\alpha&HFF&}I'll cooperate with the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuga, I'll cooperate with the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.00,0:14:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, my father proved that you're L.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.05,0:14:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll catch Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}and prove to you that I'm not Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.85,0:14:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll catch Kira, and prove to you that I'm not Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.65,0:15:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light. {\alpha&HFF&}Right now, you should be concentrating on your studies in order to join the police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.91,0:15:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light. Right now, you should be concentrating on your studies in order to join the police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.81,0:15:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can start investigating after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.61,0:15:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, father?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody knows how many years that could take.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.21,0:15:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I've already promised that... {\alpha&HFF&}if anything happens to you... I'll make sure Kira is sentenced to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.19,0:15:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I've already promised that... if anything happens to you... {\alpha&HFF&}I'll make sure Kira is sentenced to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.97,0:15:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I've already promised that... if anything happens to you... I'll make sure Kira is sentenced to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.36,0:15:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way my son is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure this can't be an act.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.69,0:15:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, {\alpha&HFF&}it's too suspicious to be an act.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.62,0:15:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's too suspicious to be an act.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.83,0:15:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, Light. {\alpha&HFF&}Kira is evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.32,0:15:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, Light. Kira is evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.02,0:15:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.02,0:15:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But recently, I've been wondering what's really to blame... {\alpha&HFF&}and it's the power to kill others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.93,0:15:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But recently, I've been wondering what's really to blame... and it's the power to kill others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any human that comes across that power will be unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.94,0:15:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how one uses that power, {\alpha&HFF&}you can never build true happiness on the deaths of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.03,0:16:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how one uses that power, you can never build true happiness on the deaths of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.30,0:16:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-san is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.82,0:16:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kira is just an ordinary person that somehow acquired these powers, {\alpha&HFF&}they are indeed unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kira is just an ordinary person that somehow acquired these powers, they are indeed unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.48,0:16:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to trouble you like this, Ryuuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best to recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.92,0:16:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm.. {\alpha&HFF&}Visiting hours are now over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm.. Visiting hours are now over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.22,0:16:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.16,0:16:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any way that I can prove to you that I'm not Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.58,0:16:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you aren't Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}then there's no need for you to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.78,0:16:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you aren't Kira, then there's no need for you to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come off it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.80,0:16:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try thinking about how it feels to be the one accused of being Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.34,0:16:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would feel awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.85,0:16:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, you could lock me up for a month, without TV or anything, {\alpha&HFF&}and keep me under supervision.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.54,0:16:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, you could lock me up for a month, without TV or anything, and keep me under supervision.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:17:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it normal for someone to want to clear their name this much?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.11,0:17:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. {\alpha&HFF&}I wouldn't do something that would infringe on your basic human rights like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.27,0:17:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I wouldn't do something that would infringe on your basic human rights like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.48,0:17:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And most importantly, it would be nonsense for me to accept the suggestion of someone who's a suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.83,0:17:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.34,0:17:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you aren't Kira, I'll find out sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, having witnessed your interaction with your father today, {\alpha&HFF&}I thought that you might not be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.87,0:17:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, having witnessed your interaction with your father today, I thought that you might not be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.03,0:17:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.77,0:17:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-{\alpha&HFF&}One last thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-One last thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'd cooperate with the investigation, {\alpha&HFF&}but until my father gets better, I don't think I can do much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.82,0:17:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'd cooperate with the investigation, but until my father gets better, I don't think I can do much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.87,0:17:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.80,0:17:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuga Hideki... {\alpha&HFF&}Ryuuzaki... he's the L I've been fighting all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.74,0:17:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuga Hideki... Ryuuzaki... {\alpha&HFF&}he's the L I've been fighting all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.05,0:17:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuga Hideki... Ryuuzaki... he's the L I've been fighting all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His real name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.87,0:17:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami Light... {\alpha&HFF&}are you not Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.98,0:17:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami Light... are you not Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.66,0:18:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.90,0:18:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.11,0:18:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never once thought of me finding this notebook as unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy to have this power... {\alpha&HFF&}and I'll create a perfect world with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy to have this power... and I'll create a perfect world with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.85,0:18:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care whether the notebook makes you happy or unhappy, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.31,0:18:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, {\alpha&HFF&}I've heard that normally, people who are haunted by Shinigami, usually end up unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I've heard that normally, people who are haunted by Shinigami, usually end up unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.71,0:18:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.40,0:18:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you'll get to see a pattern that's not normal then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thankful for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.32,0:18:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.00,0:18:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the best plan ya can come up with?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better not be thinking that ya can get ratings by only airing programs about Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.21,0:18:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason my channel has survived is because we air stories that other channels don't do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.07,0:19:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.96,0:19:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The problem is getting stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.79,0:19:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone bring me a good story!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say that, but the police aren't saying anything; it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! {\alpha&HFF&}If you don't have a story, who cares if it's a fake, just make one up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.31,0:19:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! If you don't have a story, who cares if it's a fake, just make one up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.56,0:19:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Director Demegawa, {\alpha&HFF&}there's a special delivery for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.15,0:19:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Director Demegawa, there's a special delivery for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.06,0:19:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.31,0:19:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this from?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.93,0:19:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the kind of stuff I need ya guys to come up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:41.66,LongNote,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}Along with proving\Nthe fact that I am Kira\Na message from Kira to the world\Nwill also be broadcast.\NIf you don't air this,\NI will kill off your company,\Nbeginning with the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.75,0:19:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.26,0:19:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A message from Kira to the world
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"If you don't air this, I will kill off your company, starting off with the president", apparently!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.62,0:19:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'd dare to oppose this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.96,0:19:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is real, it's going to be amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so excited, my heart's pumping like mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.12,0:19:56.95,LongNote,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)}To Director Demegawa\N- Sakura TV\N\NI am Kira.\N\NProof is provided in video tape one.\N\NOnce you've ascertained that I am Kira,\Nplease air tapes two to four on the\Ndates listed on the next page from your station.\N\NBy fore-warning people of these murders,\Nalong with proving to society the fact that\NI am Kira.
